    public class MachineImpl
extends DynamicDeviceImpl
implements Machine
    An implementation of the model object 'Machine Adapter'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Mach Type
    • Speed
    • Angle
    • Efd
    • Pm
    • Pe
    • QGen
    • FG
    • Parent Gen
    • Mach Data
    • Controller List
    • Pe Neg Seq
